^I^I^I&nbsp;










SHR




^Imemory, immediate
^IREG, immediate
^Imemory, CL
^IREG, CL




Shift operand1 Right. The number of shifts is set by operand2.

Algorithm:


^IShift all bits right, the bit that goes off is set to CF.
^IZero bit is inserted to the left-most position.


Example:MOV AL, 00000111b
SHR AL, 1         ; AL = 00000011b,  CF=1.

RET



 C O 
 r r 


OF=0 if first operand keeps original sign.

TOP
